These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: fanta, mirinda, soy-milk, 7up
Sport: baseball, handball, cricket, skiing
1. Beverage:fanta is on the right of Sport:cricket##1
2. Sport:skiing is on the far left##1
3. Sport:cricket is between Sport:handball and Beverage:mirinda##2
4. Beverage:7up is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:soy-milk is between Beverage:mirinda and Beverage:fanta##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | 7up         | mirinda   | soy-milk | fanta       |
| Sport      | skiing | baseball | cricket   | handball |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: sudoku, collecting, card-games, camping
Nationality: indian, french, nigerian, indonesian
1. Nationality:indonesian is between Hobby:card-games and Nationality:french##2
2. Hobby:camping is on the far right##1
3. Nationality:nigerian is on the right of Nationality:indian##1
4. Hobby:sudoku is on the left of Nationality:indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | collecting | sudoku | card-games | camping |
| Nationality   | french    | indonesian   | indian | nigerian       |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
