2. Nationality:brazilian is between Nationality:japanese and Food:plum##2
3. Nationality:japanese is on the far left##1
4. Nationality:egyptian is on the left of Food:asparagus##1
5. Food:plum == Nationality:egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | blueberry    | grapes | plum   | asparagus  |
| Nationality   | japanese | brazilian   | egyptian | pakistani |

